ğŸ“¦ Installation
Backend Setup

git clone https://github.com/Bhuvansai-16/Grammar_Checker.git
cd grammar-checker/backend
uvicorn main:app --reload for FastAPI

Frontend Setup
cd ../frontend
npm install
npm run dev
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ğŸ” How It Works
User enters or uploads text.

Backend processes the text using NLP models to detect and correct grammar.

The corrected text is returned to the frontend.

Errors are highlighted and users can preview/download results.
